Introduction

Universe, also known as the 2nd Generation 'Universe', is a StelLive subunit that includes four members: Shirayuki Hina, Neneko Mashiro, Akane Lize, and Arahashi Tabi.

They debuted in February 2024 along with the mini-album 'Milky Way'.
